<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Ariana Diaries</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin:
      0; padding: 0; color: #3f3210; } .container { width: 100%; max-width:
      600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header {
      text-align: center; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; }
      .header img { max-width: 150px; } .content { padding: 20px; } .content h1
      { color: #d4af37; /* Gold color */ } .content p { font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; } .button { display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; color: #fff; background-color:
      #d4af37; /* Gold color */ text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s; } .button:hover { background-color:
      #b9952d; } .footer { text-align: center; padding: 10px 0; color: #6d602f;
      font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea; margin-top: 20px; }
      .footer p { margin: 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Ariana Diaries Logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Hello {{name}},</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Ariana Diaries! We're thrilled to have you join our
          community.</p>
        <p>
          Ariana Diaries is your go-to destination for a diverse range of
          lifestyle products. Whether you're looking for exquisite jewelry,
          trendy clothing, stylish bags, or even tickets to the latest events,
          we've got you covered.
        </p>
        <p>
          Get ready to embark on a life-changing journey filled with exclusive
          deals, inspirational content, and a vibrant community of like-minded
          individuals. We're here to make every moment special and every
          purchase memorable.
        </p>
        <p>
          Start exploring now and discover the endless possibilities that await
          you at Ariana Diaries. Click the button below to dive right in!
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="https://www.arianadiaries.com" class="button">Explore Ariana
            Diaries</a>
        </p>
        <p>Best Regards,<br />The Ariana Diaries Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Ariana Diaries. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>